- [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/)
- [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- [React Router DOM](https://reactrouter.com/)
- [Axios](https://axios-http.com/)
- [React Hot Toast](https://react-hot-toast.com/)
